<doc id="320630" wikidata="Q944511" url="?curid=320630" title="Sorachi Subprefecture">
<text>is a subprefecture of Hokkaido Prefecture, Japan. As of 2004, its estimated population is 373,736 and its area is 6,558.26 km2.

