<doc id="320680" wikidata="Q1137454" url="?curid=320680" title="Tokachi Subprefecture">
<text>is a subprefecture of Hokkaido Prefecture, Japan corresponding to the old province of Tokachi. As of 2004, its estimated population is 360,802 and its area is 10,830.99 km2.

Tokachi-Obihiro Airport is in the city of Obihiro.

