<doc id="320681" wikidata="Q1141563" url="?curid=320681" title="Kushiro Subprefecture">
<text>is a subprefecture of Hokkaido Prefecture, Japan. Kushiro is home to a population of red-crowned cranes, estimated in 2022 to number about 1,900.

== Geography ==

